04/28/2025
    - small balancing changes; gave PC higher start HP, dodge, and defense
    - items (lights) can now influence the PC's view distance
    - Starting on main menu
04/29/2025
    - Game can now 'loop'; when game ends, user can elect to start again w/o returning to terminal.
    - Main menu now has a window for displaying all the monster types; each type gets a scrollable page
    - Main menu now has a window for displaying all the item types; each type gets a scrollable page
    - Main menu now has a window for display some directions (story + controls)
04/30/2025
    - created function for printing distance maps to NCurses screen for debugging
    - 'z' to show distance maps; both walk/tunnel master copies on turn + monster path on monster inspect
05/01/2025
    - Fixed pathMove bug; I was mixing UINT8_t and INT8_t, which lead to errors.
    - Fixed player_c destructor to prevent memory leak on carried / equipped items
    - Updated controls page to reflect distance map / monster path binding
05/04/2025
    - Fixed 'Level Clear' message overwriting item pickup message
